ade a thousand mistakes, but we knew that when we =E2=80=94 the first time =
we did business in India, I flew back and I said, =E2=80=9CThis is a nightm=
are, but it=E2=80=99s a nightmare we want to go after, it=E2=80=99s what we=
 do for a living as a company. We need to set up an entity there, we need t=
o find the right talent. We need to move into those countries and do it our=
selves.=E2=80=9D I personally lived in China, our president and COO moved t=
o Africa, we=E2=80=99ve had people moving all around the globe because key =
markets are places where doing business, it=E2=80=99s hard, otherwise someo=
